reviewText: It left me with desiring more.  Wish it was longer and more thorough and more teaching.
Jack Hayford did a marvelous job of presenting our Lord Jesus and our beloved Israel. I have loved this Documentary since in was out in VHF. I finally found it in DVD. You will not be disappointed!!
There was way too much preaching in this video and not enough video of place where Jesus really did live and walk.  I was disappoined to say the least.
This has the greatest pictures of a place we dream of going to one day thank you
